tories.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">• Agile Methodology:</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Work in collaboration with cross-functional Agile teams to ensure the timely delivery of high-quality</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">solutions.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Participate in Agile ceremonies such as sprint planning, daily stand-ups, sprint reviews, and</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">retrospectives.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">• Jira Proficiency:</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Utilize Jira for project management, issue tracking, and collaboration within the Agile framework.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Manage and update project backlogs, user stories, and tasks in Jira to ensure accurate and up-to-date</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">information.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">• Data Analytics:</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Apply data analysis techniques to extract meaningful insights, identify trends, and support data-</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">driven decision-making.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Collaborate with stakeholders to define key performance indicators (KPIs) and develop reports and</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">dashboards.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">• Application Development Collaboration:</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Bridge the gap between business stakeholders and development teams by effectively communicating</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">requirements, priorities, and project goals.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Collaborate with software developers and QA teams throughout the development life cycle to ensure</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">alignment with business objectives.