 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We are seeking a highly skilled Appian Low-Code Technical Lead to architect and drive the delivery of complex banking solutions. This leadership role requires deep expertise in Appian, proven experience in banking workflows, and strong people management skills. You will work closely with senior stakeholders, lead development teams, and ensure adherence to best practices, compliance, and governance standards.</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\">Key Responsibilities :</b></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Lead the architecture, design, and implementation of enterprise-grade Appian solutions.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Manage cross-functional Appian delivery teams, ensuring timely and quality delivery.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Act as a technical advisor and ensure compliance with banking industry regulations.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Define coding standards, governance practices, and reusable frameworks.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Collaborate with stakeholders to understand business needs and translate them into scalable</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">solutions.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Ensure solutions address compliance, audit, and regulatory requirements within the banking</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">sector.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Drive DevOps, CI/CD pipeline integration, and deployment automation for Appian</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">applications.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Provide guidance and mentorship to senior and junior developers.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Engage in client-facing discussions, solution demonstrations, and project sign-offs.</p><p><br></p>','<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\">Required Skills &amp; Qualifications :</b></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Bachelors/Masters in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- 6+ years of IT experience with at least 3+ years in Appian development and delivery.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Appian Level 3 Certification / Lead Designer Certification highly preferred.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Strong expertise in process modeling, records, rules, interfaces, plug-ins, and integrations.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Hands-on experience in Banking &amp; Financial Services domain with focus on compliance and</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">audit.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Proven track record of leading teams, managing stakeholders, and delivering large-scale</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Appian projects.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Knowledge of Agile methodologies, DevOps practices, and CI/CD.<br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- Strong communication, leadership, and stakeholder management skills.</p>','BE/MCA','4-8',1,2,NULL,1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Initiated',NULL,NULL,'388',8,'Chennai','Yes',1,396,396,'2025-10-08 09:54:32','2026-01-22 12:03:49'),(49,'REQ/049',NULL,NULL,NULL,4,18,14,3,1,0,NULL,'ODI, ETL, SQL, Oracle Database&nbsp;','Degree','4-6',2,1,NULL,1,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Initiated',NULL,NULL,'379',1,'Chennai','No',1,322,322,'2025-10-17 06:45:11','2025-10-17 06:45:11'),(50,'REQ/050',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,14,61,1,1,0,NULL,'Accounts, GST, TAlly','Degree','0-4',1,1,NULL,1,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Initiated',NULL,NULL,'379',8,NULL,'No',1,322,322,'2025-10-17 07:06:35','2025-10-17 07:06:35'),(51,'REQ/051',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,15,63,1,1,0,'<span data-teams=\"true\"><p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Experience in <b>B2B marketing for IT products and services</b>.</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Demonstrated success in <b>lead generation</b>, <b>marketing automation</b>, and <b>campaign execution</b>.</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Proficient in tools such as <b>LinkedIn Sales Navigator</b>, <b>ZoomInfo</b>, <b>CRM platforms</b>, <b>email marketing tools</b>, and <b>Google Analytics</b>.</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Strong understanding of global markets, especially <b>Middle East, Asia Pacific, and US</b>.</p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Excellent communication and storytelling skills – ability to create compelling content and articulate product value.</p><p style=\"margin-